How to execute:
==============

1. Go to the project folder

2. execute this command on terminal.
------------------------------------ 
 sh invertedindexing.sh
------------------------------------
3. Then it will asks for the path of the folder to be indexed,give the path of a folder containing text files. For example, inputfiles.zip contains sample text files to be indexed. Extract this, and give its name as path of a folder. 
4. After indexing is done, give input query.
5. If query  match, all the doc containing that query will be shown.For example,give the word as bhagat singh.
